() => {
		GetBinCarriers.run()
		return GetStocktakeJobOrder.run()
		.then(() => GetJobOrderJobResponses.run())
		.then(() => GetStockOnHand.run())
		.then(() => GetStocktakeCounts.run())
		.then(() => Format.createQuantities())
		.then(() => Format.createMissing())
		.then(() => Format.createUnexpected())
		.then(() => Format.createValid())
		.then(() => Format.createErrored())
	}
